Interface ProcessInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseElement, BonitaObject, NamedElement, Serializable

    public interface ProcessInstance
extends NamedElement, BaseElement
    Represents a running instance of a process. Gives access to the information of the instance, whereas the state, the definition of the process instance...
